Fill in the associated text box and click the '''Add''' button to create a new [http://wiki.wontology.org/wiki/help.php?title=Help:GlossaryAtoO#anchor_Connection connection] for the current [http://wiki.wontology.org/wiki/help.php?title=Help:GlossaryAtoO#anchor_Item item].  The connection is created from the current item "to" the constant value you supplied.

You have to click '''Add''' after entering a value in order for it to be stored.  Each '''Add''' button is independent, and only saves the information it is immediately associated with; you cannot fill in multiple connection-creation controls and then save them all with a single '''Add'''.
